        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/william_kelley/{size}/2314_2.png",
        "created_at": "2021-08-06T20:44:23.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Looking back at my notes, it seems that I wrote that Hebrart told me he was planning to do the NV 1er Cru BdB as Extra-Brut when I last visited. I guess he decided to cover both bases, but I doubt a few grams of sugar makes much difference to what is a lovely wine. FWIW, I certainly didn\u2019t think the EB needed any more sugar, but nor, I\u2019m sure, would it harm it.</p>",
